trans-unit.source: Represents a reference to a field.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en referanse til et felt.

trans-unit.source: CodeFieldReferenceExpression can be used to represent a reference to a field.
trans-unit.target: CodeFieldReferenceExpression kan brukes til å representere en referanse til et felt.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.TargetObject%2A> property specifies the object that contains the field.
The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.FieldName%2A> property specifies the name of the field to reference.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.FieldName%2A>egenskapen angir navnet på feltet å referere til.</xref:System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression.FieldName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression"></xref> class using the specified target object and field name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeFieldReferenceExpression"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av angitte objekt og feltet målnavnet.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the object that contains the field.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som angir objektet som inneholder feltet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the name of the field to reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir navnet på feltet å referere til.

trans-unit.source: A string containing the field name.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder navnet på feltet.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the object that contains the field to reference.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir objektet som inneholder felt å referere til.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"></xref> that indicates the object that contains the field to reference.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeExpression"> </xref> som angir objektet som inneholder felt å referere til.
